Class FunctionEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.math.complex.FunctionEvaluator

  • public final class FunctionEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements an iterative evaluator for FUNCTION_DATA described in ComplexOperations, making heavy use of string replacement;
